<author>d/ zkryạ ʿwḍ ạllh, rynạ wdyʿ</author>
<title>ḥyn ạ̉dnw lḥmạk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥyn ạ̉dnw lḥmạk fy ạtḍạʿ wkẖsẖwʿ ạ̉skb flby ạ̹lyk fy sjwd yạ yswʿ
 ạ̹n qlby yạ ạ̹lhy lḥḍwrk yjwʿ ạ̉rny wjhk rby ạ̉nt wḥdk yswʿ
 ạlqrạr - hllwyạ hllwyạ mjdạaⁿ llậb ạlʿẓym lk rby yjtẖw qlby wygẖny bạltrnym
 hllwyạ hllwyạ ṣwty yʿlw bạlnsẖyd bskyb ṭyb qlby ạ̉ʿbd rby ạlmjyd hllwyạ
 2- mhmạ ạ̉sẖdw lk rby ḥbk fạq ạlʿlạ qd bdẖlt ạldm ʿny ạ̉y ḥb qd ḥlạ
 ạ̉y wṣf lk rby yṣf ḥbk lạ ạ̹ny mbhwr bḥb qd smạ mạ ạ̉jmlạ
 3- ʿạbdạaⁿ ạ̉sẖdw wqlby yhtf : ạ̉nt msyḥy ṣrt mlkạ lk rby lk fwq ạlmdẖbḥ
 dmk gẖṭy̱ ly̱ ʿyby hyạ yạ nfsy ạ̉frḥy ! hllwyạ lk ḥby bk dwmạaⁿ frḥy</lyrics>
</song>